which is not the latest by the way (it is 1.0.15), [uses](https://github.com/gluonhq/substrate/blob/master/src/main/java/com/gluonhq/substrate/Constants.java#L111) the JavaFX static SDK 19-ea+8.

However, the [issue](Map, FlatMap and OrElse fluent bindings for ObservableValue) that added this new API was merged only before 19-ea+10 was released.

Until a new version of the GluonFX plugin is released with JavaFX 19 GA or the new 20-ea versions, you can simply set your plugin to use them with [`javafxStaticSdkVersion`](https://docs.gluonhq.com/#_javafxstaticsdkversion):

